claim: Hayden Panettiere played Claire Bennet on Heroes.
premise_source_doc_sentence: She is known for her roles as cheerleader Claire Bennet on the NBC sci-fi series Heroes  (  2006 -- 10  )  , Juliette Barnes in the ABC/CMT musical-drama series Nashville  (  2012 -- present  )  and Kairi in the video game series Kingdom Hearts .
